query.selectQuery: SELECT transform("eiel_c_en"."GEOMETRY" , ?T) as "GEOMETRY","eiel_c_en"."id","eiel_c_en"."id_municipio","eiel_c_en"."clave","eiel_c_en"."codprov","eiel_c_en"."codmunic","eiel_c_en"."codentidad","eiel_c_en"."codpoblamiento","eiel_c_en"."orden_en","eiel_c_en"."precision_dig","eiel_c_en"."observ" FROM "eiel_c_en" WHERE "eiel_c_en"."id_municipio" in (?M) AND "eiel_c_en"."clave"<>'AN'
